title: SE1 presents Bar Wars - Volume 1: mixed by miDJe
description:
This is Bar Wars, a brand new mix series brought to you by MC Enemy and MC Static. Volume 1 is mixed by Chemical Generation's miDJe.

This mix is put together purely for the ravers, showcasing the best in Hardcore MC's.

Future episodes will feature guest DJ's and MC's, and will be available on iTunes,Facebook, DontStayIn.com and Direct HTTP Download.

Remember, Bar Wars is all about the MC's, so if you don't appreciate what an MC does, you will not like this mix.
